      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 12,
      "chapterTitle": "三．南征北伐",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "927128_12_1361-1412",
          "range": "1361-1412",
          "rangeStart": 1361,
          "rangeEnd": 1412,
          "markText": "红军起事后，元朝正规军队完全无用。真正肯打仗的是义军，是由地主巨绅所组织的保卫私家财产生命的地方民兵。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714646435,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 18:40:35",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927128&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1361&rangeEnd=1412",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b9032ea05e2598b900f7777?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=1361&rangeEnd=1412"
        },
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "927128_12_5617-5705",
          "range": "5617-5705",
          "rangeStart": 5617,
          "rangeEnd": 5705,
          "markText": "不如用斫树的法子，先去枝叶，再挖老根，先取山东，撤掉大都的屏风，回师下河南，断掉它的羽翼，进据潼关，占领了它的门户，军事要点都拿到手了，再进围大都，那时势孤援绝，自然不战可取了",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714646433,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 18:40:33",
          "chapterUid": 12,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927128&chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5617&rangeEnd=5705",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b9032ea05e2598b900f7777?chapterUid=12&rangeStart=5617&rangeEnd=5705"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 9,
      "chapterTitle": "三．大元帅、大丞相",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "927128_9_7502-7531",
          "range": "7502-7531",
          "rangeStart": 7502,
          "rangeEnd": 7531,
          "markText": "徽州的老儒朱升，告诉元璋三句话：“高筑墙，广积粮，缓称王。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714646434,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 18:40:34",
          "chapterUid": 9,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927128&chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7502&rangeEnd=7531",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b9032ea05e2598b900f7777?chapterUid=9&rangeStart=7502&rangeEnd=7531"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "chapterUid": 10,
      "chapterTitle": "第三章 从吴国公到吴王",
      "items": [
        {
          "type": "highlight",
          "bookmarkId": "927128_10_6234-6540",
          "range": "6234-6540",
          "rangeStart": 6234,
          "rangeEnd": 6540,
          "markText": "愚闻取天下者必有一定之规模，韩信初见高祖，画楚、汉成败；孔明卧草庐，与先主论三分形势者是也。今之规模，宜北绝李察罕，南并张九四（士诚），抚温、台，取闽、越，定都建康，拓地江、广，进则越两淮以北征，退则画长江而自守。夫金陵古称龙蟠虎踞，帝王之都，借其兵力资财，以攻则克，以守则固，百察罕能如吾何哉！江之所备，莫急上流，今义师已克江州，足蔽全吴，况自滁、和至广陵（今江苏扬州），皆吾所有，非直守江，兼可守淮矣。张氏倾覆，可坐而待，淮东诸郡，亦将来归。北略中原，李氏可并也。今闻察罕妄自尊大，致书明公，如曹操之招孙权，窃以元运将终，人心不属，而察罕欲效操所为，事势不侔。宜如鲁肃计，鼎足江东，以观天下之衅。此其大纲也。",
          "colorStyle": 1,
          "colorLabel": "",
          "createTime": 1714646434,
          "createTimeFormatted": "2024-05-02 18:40:34",
          "chapterUid": 10,
          "appLink": "weread://bestbookmark?bookId=927128&chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6234&rangeEnd=6540",
          "webLink": "https://weread.qq.com/web/reader/b9032ea05e2598b900f7777?chapterUid=10&rangeStart=6234&rangeEnd=6540"
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
